name: Green-turned Eucalyptus Bowl
description:
Eucalyptus wood hand turned & finished bowl.  This is a beautiful piece of wood turned very fresh.  Eucalyptus is renowned for being very wet and for moving a lot as it dries.  This started out as a perfectly round bowl but has warped and moved to find it's own shape.  It's very tactile and has settled into a lovely organic shape.  **It's fairly dry now but may move more, especially if your home is warmer or drier than mine. This may include cracking and splitting as well as warping and moving.  This is a natural process.  The wood came from a tree surgeon friend who removed an overgrown tree for a customer.

It's finished with walnut oil.

155mm x 135mm 'diameter' x 70mm high

All of the wood I use for my bowls comes from trees grown in the UK from sustainable sources.  The majority of it comes from my own garden – either trimmings or from trees removed as part of regular management.  Other wood comes from friends and neighbours who have had trees trimmed or removed.  A few bowls are made from wood bought from a supplier of bowl blanks – this is not a source I use any more, not for any environmental or other concerns, simply because I have a very good stock of more local wood now.  For the future I intend that all of the wood I use will be local and that the source and reason for felling will be verifiable.  This provenance is important to me as far too man y trees are felled for no good reason without being replaced.

My bowls are all turned on a lathe and finished by hand.  They are not perfect specimen pieces – they are real pieces of wood complete with marks, knots, cracks, twists and warps.  Many are turned ‘green’ (which means fairly fresh after being cut and still quite wet) and as such will continue to dry and find their final shape for some time yet.  This is a natural process and only adds to the unique character of each individual piece.

They are all finished with either wax or oil, see the in individual descriptions for each bowl.  They are ‘food safe’ for use as fruit bowls but I would not recommend using them to eat from.  They would benefit from the occasional waxing (standard furniture wax is fine) or oiling (walnut oil from the supermarket is good), just a light wipe is fine to keep them looking their best.

Don’t  soak in water (wipe with a damp cloth and dry straight away) and avoid direct sunlight for any extended period.  Do pick them up regularly and hold them, feel them and enjoy them!

name: CANNA THERAPY Cannabis Cream With Full Plant Extract- anti-inflammatory, antibacterial, regenerating and rejuvenating effect
description:
Why hemp cosmetics?

Leave the soft drugs prejudices aside and take a look at cannabis from a different perspective. Despite the notoriety of plant’s reputation, it has proven medicinal and cosmetic qualities. Hemp products are highly valued natural cosmetics. Do you wonder why?

The antiseptic, antibacterial and energizing characteristics of the herb are known to man for centuries. Since ancient times, hemp was widely used against herpes, eczema and various rashes as well as skin problems of any kind.

Hemp seeds are not marijuana seeds

Now is the time to make an important clarification: Hemp seeds are not marijuana seeds, confusing both is common misconception. All types of hemp used in the food, textile and cosmetic industries are specifically cultivated Cannabis crosses generally called industrial hemp. The plant has three major subtypes: Cannabis Sativa, Cannabis Indica and Cannabis Ruderalis. Those designed for everyday use are selected as not to contain (or contain negligible amounts) of the psychoactive substance THC, which is the substance marijuana owes its effect to. It is important to know regarding hemp seed and the seed oil extract, that THC is located in the flowers of the plant not in its seeds.

What makes the hemp oil valuable?

Hemp oil contains more natural essential fatty acids than any other oil extracted from plants in perfect ratio 3:1 - Omega-6: Omega-3. Contains vitamin E which is a natural antioxidant. Gamma-linolenic acid (GLA) is very close in composition to the fat cells in the human body. This makes cannabis extract unique for deep hydration of skin cell structures as our body does not manufacture these acids by itself. Hemp also contains a complex of vitamins A, B, C, D and E, essential to skin care. It provides the skin with effective sun protection during summer, and reduces the effects of cold-warm transition or vice versa during winter.

Hemp oil has an exceptional effect:

Moisturizes the skin and brings it to a new life; makes tan uniform; regenerates cells;
Protects against the harmful effects of the environment - wind, sun, UV rays, pollution.
Has an anti-inflammatory effect. Highly suitable for dry and devitalized skin; with problems such as acne, eczema, psoriasis.

Whom is hemp cosmetics suitable for?

Natural hemp cosmetics in the form of creams and ointments protect the skin cells from the adverse external conditions by taking care of the water preservation in the cells, preventing from premature aging. A great advantage is the delicacy of the cannabis extract, making it suitable for sensitive and allergic skin prone to acne.

Daily use of the hemp cosmetics has primarily a preventive cosmetic function, but has also a favorable effect on some common skin diseases such as atopic eczema, psoriasis or acne.

The Canna Therapy cream

The Canna Therapy cream is prepared using advanced technology based on lipophilic-acrylic matrix that reduces irritating emulsifiers. The texture of the Canna Therapy cream is very light, absorbs instantly, does not irritate the skin and leaves no greasy residue. Thanks to its BIO formula, the cream does not contain any petroleum products or animal products, solvents, sulfates, silicones, paragons and artificial colors. Cold pressed hemp oil contains essential fatty acids and gamma-linolenic acid, which takes care of the development of the natural barrier function of the skin.

We have combined the hemp oil carefully with organic unrefined oils from macadamia, almond and rose at a controlled temperature, so as to retain the natural bioactive properties of the oils. Along with the hydrating ingredients such as glycerin, panthenol, valuable natural oils form almond, rose and macadamia the cream is enriched with natural UV filters, protective vitamin E and regenerating and Anti-aging BIO serum. The Canna Therapy cream is suitable for daily care for all skin types, even if very sensitive or problematic skin.


The Canna Therapy cosmetics are unique containing not only hemp oil, but also Cannabis Sativa extract - a source of unsaturated fatty acids, phospholipids and phytosterols, range natural antioxidants, biominerals, vitamins, carotenoids and chlorophylls. Facial cream Canna Therapy has antibacterial, anti-inflammatory, antiallergenic and regenerating effect. The product has positive effects on various dermatitis, atopic eczema, psoriasis and acne. By its nourishing natural ingredients the Canna Therapy cream provides a natural protective film for easily irritated and sensitive skin prone to dryness and cracking. The cream contains vitamin B8 inositol vitamin of youth, vitality and health with superb biostimulating and antioxidant effect.


While Carnosine prevents glycation of proteins and keeps skin "forever young" cyclic pentapeptide and ceramides are involved in the renovation, preservation and hydration of the skin cell structures. The skin becomes smooth, elastic, tight and silky. Anti-age complex gradually smooth out wrinkles, makes tan uniform and ameliorates the skin structure, leaving the skin beautiful and with optimal level of hydration.

name: Honey infused with Strawberries and Serranos
description:
Spicy honey is a unique condiment great on cheese plates, toast, pizza, wings, eggs, peanut butter, and even ice cream. The honey evens out the heat from the chilies and lets you enjoy their unique flavor profiles while still giving you bit of a kick. Great for the heat seekers in your life.

Originally this flavor was “Strawberry Jalepeno,” but it wasn’t long after we decided that just wasn’t spicy enough for us. Earthy Serranos balance out super sweet Strawberrys to make a honey thats got the perfect balance of heat and sweet. Almost a desert condiment this honey is especially great on toast, cornbreads, and pastries.

Ingredients: 12oz Pure USA Honey, Serrano Chilies, Strawberries

name: The Contender
description:
Varnished acrylic painting on stretched canvas with painted edges ready to hang on your wall.

No frame required as it's a deep canvas.

W 107 cm,  L 76.5 cm, depth of the canvas 4,5 cm

I met and observed a two year old bay colt in a local stud which I was invited to before he was moved on to begin a race career in England. When he was brought out straight away I thought that he was a Rock star , the way he moved and he had a great presence about him and after getting a number of photograph's I could not get to my canvas fast enough to try and capture the essence of this horse. I called him The Contender as I thought it was fitting considering he was about to embark on a journey to try being a working athlete in the horse race industry and I do hope he has a long and safe career. He really is a beauty and I was very happy with the way I caught him in this painting.

name: Pink Bible Study Notes Printable for traveler's notebook and Fauxdori, Faithdori, Bible journaling, Bible art journaling
description:
This is a digital file for a standard size fauxdori or travelers notebook.  The file will print on 8.5x11 paper and will need trimmed to size (2.75 bottom margin).  The file should be printed front and back, trimmed, and then stapled together in the center to form a booklet.

You are not purchasing a finished product.  You must download the file to print your own insert.

The Bible study planner is great for keeping track of your notes in personal or small group Bible studies.  It can be used if you are studying a book of the Bible, or if you are studying a separate book or devotional.  There is a box at the top to list the book and/or author.  On the left side of the page is a box titled "Big Idea." Below that is a box marked "Key Passages," a perfect place to write in a Bible verse or page number.  On the right side of the page is a Notes column.  And across the bottom is a white box for journaling inspiration.

Because I read my Bible and all other books on my Kindle, I needed a place to write my notes for Bible study where I could easily reference them.  And I'm always getting Bible journaling inspiration when I'm reading.  Now I have one place to keep them all.

If you would like the Bible Study Notes printable in a different color, please message me about a special order.

name: Ace of Spades – Motörhead / Lemmy
description:
A vinyl art tribute to one of the “last true rock stars” Ian Fraser Kilmister. Better known as Lemmy, the Staffordshire-born musician who was the bassist and lead vocalist of the heavy metal band Motörhead.

This vinyl artwork features their hit single “Ace of Spades” which was released by Bronze during Motörhead’s career high point in 1980.

Probably their best known song, “Ace of Spades” spent 13 weeks in the UK Singles Chart, and originally peaked at number 15 upon its initial release and consisted of a pounding bass line and gambling metaphors.

Mixed media on print. Including 2 original 'Ace of Spades' 7" Singles.

Dimensions: Length: 550mm Height: 550mm Depth: 50mm

Presented in a black framed box

Limited Edition of 10, signed and numbered by myself, the artist

name: Ukrainian traditional doll-motanka /Кукла-мотанка "Кубышка-травница"
description:
Кукла-мотанка Кубышка-травница
Кубышка -травница – это настоящий символ уюта и добра в доме. Она наполнена душистыми травами, дарит домочадцам умиротворение, радость и гармонию, отгоняя серые мысли и грусть. Очень уютная и душевная куколка.
Кукла – мотанка Травница не впускает в дом болезнь.
Наполнена сборами душистых лекарственных трав. Ее подвешивали либо над постелью больного, либо над колыбелью новорожденного. В последнем случае, Травница также помогала отогнать злых духов от младенца, к тому же служила для ребенка забавой. Мамы перед сном разминали куклу, и тогда аромат трав усиливался, успокаивая малыша и даруя ему здоровый сон.
Окунувшись в аромат Кубышки-Травницы, мы обретаем душевный покой, легкость дыхания и ясность мысли.
Кубышка наполнена мятой,мелиссой,лавандой и валерьяной.
Мята перечная -и успокаивает, и тонизирует (в зависимости от количества), лечит нервные расстройства, а также стимулирует работу мозга, дарит спокойный сон.
Лаванда – успокоительное средство как для нервной системы, так и для дыхательных путей,очищает воздух и убивает болезнетворные бактерии. А еще лаванда способна подарить любовь и счастье, увеличить взаимопонимание и избавить дом от негативной энергии.
Валериана – поднимает настроение, помогает обрести гармонию,улучшает атмосферу жилища, снижает количество ссор и помогает достичь взаимопонимания.
Мелисса -пПомогает при снижении умственной и физической работоспособ­ности, меланхолии,повышает опти­мизм, способствует удаче в жизни, укрепляет меха­низмы энергетического регулирования.
Эта куколка привнесет в дом и семью взаимопонимание и согласие, поэтому набор трав в ней не случайный :)
Кубышка-травница– прекрасный и очень уютный подарок друзьям, родным и близким.

name: Custom, Personalized Despicable Me Minion Birthday Invitation with child's picture
description:
Welcome to Fehlinger Graphics!

This listing is for a 5x7 print ready digital file of a Custom, Personalized Despicable Me Minion Birthday Invitation with child's picture. After ordering, this invitation will be personalized with your event details and then a digital file will be emailed to you. You can then print at the printer of your choice. Fehlinger Graphics also offers print and mail services upon request.


***NOTICE: This listing is for a digital file ONLY.
>>> NO PHYSICAL ITEMS WILL BE SHIPPED <<<

Why order a digital file?...
• Fast turnaround
• No shipping fees
• Save money by printing at home or send to your favorite print center
• Print exact number of invitations needed
• Ability to email to friends and family

---- How to Order - Despicable Me Minion Birthday Party Invitation ----
1. Click "Add to Cart" to begin purchase process.

2. Add all of your event details in the "Note to Fehlinger Graphics" box at checkout.
Including:
• name
• age
• location / address
• day of week, date, time
• RSVP info (optional) - exact wording please

3. Once payment and all of your event details are received your invitation will be personalized. A high resolution NON-EDITABLE 5x7 digital jpg file will then be emailed to you within 1 to 3 business days.

4. Upon receipt, please review design and proof read invitation carefully for any spelling mistakes. If you are not completely satisfied let us know and we will make any small changes at no additional fees within 2 weeks of sale.

5. If acceptable, you are ready to print! You can print at home, send to your favorite print shop, or simply email out to friends and family!

For best results, print on white cardstock.

***Note that printed colors may not match exactly due to varieties in paper quality, computer monitor setting, and printer quality.

Please feel free to contact us with any questions about this Despicable Me Minion Birthday Invitation!

Thanks!

name: Observer
description:
The name says it all, the expression in the eye could make you believe that perhaps what is been observed is not something nearby but more a faraway thought or a memory,pondering.

Acrylic paint on stretched canvas with a varnish finish. A deep painted edge canvas.

W 31 cm L 35 cm depth 4.5 cm

With the luxury of having access to a local stud where I can go to look at , to watch , photograph and at times get quick sketches done of the horses that are there at the time, it is easy to see that these beautiful animals have such intelligence, it is not an abstract thought to express this in a painting of a horse but simply representing a fact once you see the essence and the manner with which they carry themselves and bear in mind, in a sense they are slaves so if they seem abrupt with people then the people should bring some understanding to the scene and for the most part ,thankfully they do. The more you look the more you will see.

name: Romanzo "I Racconti del Guardiano Notturno" di C. Alpini
description:
Romanzo Thriller di Christian Alpini, ambientato in un manicomio criminale
"Uno dei vecchi guardiani mi ha detto che in alcune stanze, se ti affacci allo spioncino, non riesci a vedere nessuno. Ma non perché la stanza sia vuota; semplicemente perché il paziente che c'è dentro non ha voglia di farsi vedere." Spesso il guardiano parlerà direttamente al lettore, facendolo sentire parte della vicenda e giocando spesso con lui. Racconterà la vità del manicomio durante la notte...e darà indizi velati su tutta la vicenda....insomma...non una semplice raccolta ma un vero e proprio romanzo alternativo.
Tanti segreti nascosti tra le pagine ed il lettore coinvolto in prima persona..non un semplice romanzo..ma una vera epropria esperienza.

name: Ukrainian folk doll motanka Veduchka/Кукла-мотанка "Ведучка"
description:
Кукла Ведучка оберег-в жизнь ведущая. Оберег символизирует неразрывную связь между матерью и ребенком.Кукла ведучка-это символ преемственности поколений,материнской заботы и любви.
Мама ведет свою дочь в жизнь,Учит ее всем житейским мудростям. Силой своей любви оберегает от бед и несчастий.
Это может быть образ матери, тёти, наставницы, крёстной – человека, помогающего принимать решения, идти правильной дорогой. Это и образ человека (не обязательно родственника), оказывающего поддержку в нужный момент.
Такой вот Ангел-хранитель в человеческом воплощении.
«Ведущая по жизни» – это взрослая Мудрость и Житейский Опыт, безусловная Любовь к малышу и Защита от падений… Малыш, в свою очередь, тоже опора для «Ведущей по жизни», своеобразный «двигатель» – тянет вперёд для роста и развития в жизни.
Особенность этой куколки – руки Ведучки и малыша – одна единая скатка. Это символизирует и неразрывную связь поколений, и прочную поддержку старшего младшему, и единую энергию, как Любовь и Понимание.
«Ведущая по жизни» будет прекрасным подарком как молодой маме, с пожеланием Терпения и Родительской Мудрости, так и для «взрослых» родителей – когда-то они Вас вели в жизнь, а теперь Вы, являясь опорой, помогаете им «идти и не падать» по жизни.


Doll Veduchka ward-leader in life. Charm symbolizes the unbreakable bond between mother and child.Doll veduchka is a symbol of the continuity of generations, maternal care and love.
My mother is my daughter to life, teaching her all worldly wisdom. The force of his love protects from troubles and misfortunes.
This may be a way of his mother, aunt, mentor, godmother - a person who helps make decisions to go the right way. This image of a person (not necessarily a relative), providing support at the right time.
Such is the guardian angel in a human lifetime.
"Leading for Life" - is an adult The wisdom and experience of life, unconditional love for your child, and protection from falls ... Baby, in turn, is also support for the "Leading for Life", a kind of "engine" - pulls forward for growth and development in the life .
The peculiarity of this chrysalis - hands Veduchki and baby - one single roll from overcoat. It symbolizes the unbreakable link between generations, and strong support for older younger, single, and the energy of love and understanding.
"Leading for Life" will be a wonderful gift as a young mother with a wish patience and Parent Wisdom, as well as for "adults" parents - they once you were in life, and now you are being supported, helping them to "go and do not fall "for life.

description:
This pen is the first of a collection called "Bones and Burl".  All the pens are handmade by me and include a combination of Oak or Maple Burl* and either Deer or Elk antler.



*A burl is a tree growth in which the grain has grown in a deformed manner. It is commonly found in the form of a rounded outgrowth on a tree trunk or branch that is filled with small knots from dormant buds. Burls yield a very peculiar and highly figured wood, prized for its beauty and rarity. It is sought after by furniture makers, artists, and wood sculptors. There are a number of well-known types of burls (each from a particular species); these are highly valued and sliced into veneers for furniture, inlay in doors, picture frames, household objects, automobile interior paneling and trim, and woodturning.

name: Original U.S. WWII Combat Medic 66th Infantry Division Ike Jacket and Shirt [ON3008]
description:
Original Item: On-of-a-kind. Combat medic material from WW2 is some of the hardest most collectible items on the market, due to the small number of medics in comparison to infantry soldiers. Well, we found one! This is a wonderful little grouping that belonged to a decorated veteran of WWII. He was a Technical Sergeant (T/Sgt.) Medic and a member of the 263rd Infantry Regiment, 66th Infantry Division of the 12th Army Group.

This set is composed of the following:
• Ike Jack in very good condition Size US 38L (marked Johhny)
• Four overseas combat service bars (on right sleeve cuff) meaning 24+ months of combat
• Technical Sergeant (T/Sgt.) Chevrons
• 263 66 Division INF patch on left shoulder
• Black Panther 66th Inf Div shoulder cloth patches on right shoulder
• 42nd Infantry Division “Rainbow Division” patch on left shoulder
• Black Panther 66th Inf Div enabled pins on lapels
• Very rare colored sterling silver WWII Combat Medic Badge Pin
• Sterling silver U.S. Army Sharpshooter Rifle Badge
• WWII good conduct medal
• World War II Victory Medal
• American Defense Service Medal
• The following Medal Ribbons:
- European, African, Middle East Campaign Ribbon (3 Invasion Stars)
- Army Good Conduct with double loop/knot
- Bronze Star (World War II infantry award)
- WWII Occupation Medal Ribbon
- WWII Victory Medal Ribbon
• Army relation shirt with:
- Technical Sergeant (T/Sgt.) Chevrons
- Black Panther 66th Inf Div shoulder cloth patches on right shoulder
- 42nd Infantry Division “Rainbow Division” patch on left shoulder
- Medic lapel pin


66th Infantry Division WWII Combat Chronicle:
The three regiments of the 66th Infantry Division arrived in England on 26 November 1944 and the remainder of the division on 12 December 1944, training until 24 December 1944 when the Division crossed the English Channel to Cherbourg on two Belgian steamships, the Chesire and the Leopoldville. A German torpedo ripped into the transport Leopoldville just five miles from its destination of Cherbourg, and 14 officers and 748 enlisted men were lost.

name: Original British Household Cavalry Named Life Guards Officer Cuirass and Helmet Set [ON8829]
description:
Original Items: One-of-a-kind-set. This is quality material, dating from the Reign of Queen Elizabeth II who came to the throne in 1953. Buckingham Palace in central London is the official residence of the Queen although she has many country estates. The Household Cavalry (HCav) is made up of the two most senior regiments of the British Army, the Life Guards and the Blues and Royals (Royal Horse Guards and 1st Dragoons). These regiments are divided between the Armoured Regiment stationed at Combermere Barracks in Windsor and the ceremonial mounted unit, the Household Cavalry Mounted Regiment, garrisoned at Hyde Park Barracks (Knightsbridge Barracks) in London. The Household Cavalry is part of the Household Division and is the Queen's official bodyguard.

The British Household Cavalry is classed as a corps in its own right, and consists of two regiments: the Life Guards and the Blues and Royals (Royal Horse Guards and 1st Dragoons). They are the senior regular regiments in the British Army, with traditions dating from 1660, and act as the Queen's personal bodyguard. They are guards regiments and, with the five foot guard regiments, help constitute the seven guards regiments of the Household Division.

Here we offer a complete cuirass set (chest and back plate) with helmet of Lieutenant BARLOW of the Life Guards.

Officer's Uniforms are far more elaborate than for the standard trooper uniforms. The helmet plates and mounts are gilt and the cuirasses are lined in velvet. Officer’s uniforms are very expensive with no cost spared being in the direct service of the Monarch. This set, just received from an English collection, is in excellent condition and bears Lt. BARLOW's name on the inside of the breast and back plate. A magnificent set rarely encountered.

name: Original WWII Guinness Advertising Oil on Canvas Artwork by John Gilroy - 1944 Royal Navy Submarine Crew [ON8505]
description:
Original Item: One-of-a-kind. This is a fascinating story! We've all heard of Guinness, a popular Irish dry stout that originated in the brewery of Arthur Guinness (1725–1803) at St. James's Gate, Dublin. Guinness is one of the most successful beer brands worldwide. It is brewed in nearly 60 countries and is available in over 120, with annual sales totaling 850 million liters (1.5 billion Imperial or 1.8 billion US pints).

Well, what we have here is an original oil painting by the dedicated Guinness advertising account artist John Gilroy. These painting were first created and once approved internally by the advertising agency and then the client (in this case Guinness) posters would be printed and pasted all over the UK.

This particular example is one of the very few WW2 Guinness advertisements. It reads:

GUINNESS - FOR STRENGTH


This completely authentic first generation oil painting is beautifully preserved and framed. It even still bears the original paper S.H. Benson advertising agency paper tag that is clearly dated 1944.

The tag reads as follows:

S.H. Benson
-Advertising Agency-
Client: Guinness
Account: GE/44
Artist: GILROY
Action: SUBMIT TO CENSOR



Guinness's iconic stature is partly due to its advertising, the most notable and recognizable series of advertisements was created by S.H. Benson's advertising, primarily drawn by the artist John Gilroy, in the 1930s and 1940s.

Benson created posters that included phrases such as "Guinness for Strength", "Lovely Day for a Guinness", "Guinness Makes You Strong," "My Goodness My Guinness," (or, alternatively, "My Goodness, My Christmas, It's Guinness!") and, "Guinness is Good For You". The posters featured Gilroy's distinctive artwork and more often than not featured animals such as a kangaroo, ostrich, seal, lion and notably a toucan, which has become as much a symbol of Guinness as the harp.

The genuine one-of-a-kind oil painting measures 34 inches wide by 29 inches tall. The original canvas was mounted on board and one can still see the thumbtack impressions along the margins. The painting is signed GILROY in the bottom left corner.

This particular painting depicts a sailor in the Royal Navy crossing a wooden gangplank from the wharf to a submarine with a massive torpedo slung over his shoulder. Standing beside him on the dockside is an iron stanchion with an empty glass and a bottle of Guinness next to it (as if he has just drunk it, like Popeye eats spinach).

On of the most compelling aspects of this particular work are the copious pencil notes on the canvas, presumably written by the creative account manager at S.H. Benson that read as follows:

Make figures smaller
longer torpedo
longer gang plank
find reference for Conning Tower
Add man in hatch?


A charming advertisement intended to boost morale during WW2, and one of only a very few in Gilroy’s short-lived Guinness WWII series, making it not only one-of-a-kind but extremely rare.

Included with this framed painting comes a signed copy of the 255 page book; GILROY WAS GOOD FOR GUINNESS. The book shows Gilroy’s history with Guinness and illustrates this very painting on page 177.

Gilroy was Great Britain's Norman Rockwell and a treasure trove has been discovered, over the next years the prices will skyrocket and especially on those few that have a piece from the extremely rare WW2 series.


Founded by Arthur Guinness, 1725-1803, this dark nectar was first marketed in 1778. It has climbed in popularity over the next 235 years. In 1932 it moved its headquarters from Dublin to London and was then rated the 7th largest Company in the world. On moving to London Guinness contracted with the S. H. Benson Advertising Agency and for the next thirty years one of the greatest advertising campaigns came into being. Basically this was all because of the renowned commercial artist JOHN GILROY. England's equivalent to Norman Rockwell.

For thirty years Gilroy created some of the most loved Post Advertising of all time. He created the famous Zoo Series including his use of animals, such as Ostriches, Toucans and Gnus, a WW2 Series, an Old Masters series, an Olympic series for 1948 London Games and an Exotic Automobile series as well as countless others.

The point was to promote the benefits that "Guinness was Good For You", and "Guinness For Strength", creating a truly enchanting series of Campaigns that are still near to many people's hearts.

In 1962 a new Marketing team joined Guinness and terminated its contracts with Bensons and within short order the S.H. Benson advertising agency closed down with all it's archives being placed in storage. In 2010 this came to light and over 200 original oil paintings, original works of John Gilroy, were discovered. Any Gilroy work will now become a most rewarding investment. John Gilroy Died in 1985 just a month short of his 87th birthday.

name: Original German M40 WWII Type Steel Helmet- Finnish M40/55 Contract - Scratch & Dent [GG4055SD]
description:
Original Item: These are helmets that have serious imperfections in the shell that prevents them from being sold as Grade one. Offered as is, no size selection.

In another military antiques coup, IMA has just acquired the last of all the known WWII helmet stocks (thousands!) from the government of Finland. These helmets are 100% genuine German manufactured WWII type M40 steel combat helmets that were produced by German WWII helmet manufacturer Hans Römer Fabrik from Neu-Ulm (Donau-Freiberg).

Supplied throughout WWII and then under special contract for the Finnish Army in 1955, hence, they have become known as the M40/55 helmet. However, these helmets were made in the same factory, on the same machines and by some of the very same people that produced them for Germany in WWII. They are nearly identical to WWII issue M40’s, (and are often sold as such) with the classic rolled edge, correct steel thickness, and pressed ventilation holes. Furthermore, we have very good reason to believe that some of these shells are “sanitized” German WWII M35 and M40 helmets; meaning some are genuine WWII shells that had all stampings rubbed out and original paint removed to avoid the allied ban on West Germany selling war materiel after WW2.

The leather liners and chinstraps were made in Finland for the Finnish army; styles vary, as some of the helmets were used up until the early 1970s. The shells do however, accept our splendid reproduction M35 WWII leather helmet liner and chinstrap with reproduction WW2 split pin and washer sets.

Styles and colors (Field Grey, Field Green) may vary slightly so please see photos for variation examples. These are offered in "Scratch & Dent" condition and will have significant dents, scratches, etc in the shell. These are real surplus military helmets that were used by actual soldiers in the defense of their country, and some of them did not fare as well over the years.

This is a rare chance to own a genuine military issue German made M40 WWII style helmet for the almost the same price as a Chinese or Indian made reproduction. There is simply no comparison to a genuine combat helmet!

History of Finnish Combat Helmets-
Finland imported tens of thousands of helmets for the Winter War of 1939-40 and the Continuation War of 1941-44, and imported again in 1955. Since IMA acquired the last of all the known helmet stock from the Finnish government you may wonder did we get German WWII marked helmets? Yes, and they will be offered at a far higher price. Did we get other types of helmets? Yes, we also received Hungarian WWII M38 (1938) helmets as well. This deal is a treasure trove of WWII era combat helmet history.

History the German & Finnish Alliance-
In 1938 Finland became very concerned with Stalin's Soviet expansionism and turned to Great Britain and France for support. Both Countries were under supplied themselves so Finland, perhaps reluctantly turned to Nazi Germany for aid. Hitler was swift to assist supplying great quantities of materiel including thousands of German Battle Helmets.

The Russians invaded Finland in 1939 driving deep into the country. The Finns resisted with amazing tenacity that has been the subject of legend and the wonderful WW2 Movie "THE WINTER WAR" (offered by IMA). The Russians paid a very heavy price and sued for peace in early 1940 keeping the invaded areas of Finland. Finland totally exhausted agreed with great regret.

In the summer of 1941 Hitler’s Nazi War Machine invaded the Soviet Union driving everything before them. Finland whom had received so much help from Germany then rose up and drove the Soviet presence out of Finland. However Finland would not "invade" the Soviet Union, they declared themselves not to be aggressors.

It is true however that the Germans recruited great numbers of Finnish "Volunteers" for their "SS UNITS" that did invade Mother Russia but that was true of all the overrun European Countries and even some others, still independent including apparently England and the United States, although these number were said to be very low.

At the close of WW2 with Germany defeated Finland was highly penalized by the Soviet Union, again gave up the lost territory of 1939/40 but did manage to retain it's independence unlike so much of Eastern Europe.

name: Cirino's Bloody Mary Mix
description:
A CONCENTRATE: use only 1 oz. to make 1 Bloody Mary/32oz. bottle=32 Bloody Mary drinks.

COST-EFFECTIVE: .62 per Bloody Mary/No waste as our Mix is the entire spice base of a Bloody Mary. Not pre-mixed w/ tomato juice thus, does not go bad in the refrigerator.

CONSISTENT: same fresh Bloody Mary every time. You add the tomato juice and adult beverage. No metallic or oxidized taste from pre-mixed tomato juice going rancid.

CONVENIENT: 3-Easy Steps. Pour 1 oz. of our Mix, 1 oz. of adult beverage and 4 oz. of tomato juice into 10-13 oz. glass filled with ice.

A MARINADE: our Mix is an acid-base product. Delicious as a marinade for meat, chicken, fish, vegetables, etc. or flavor base for soups, sauces, dips, meatloaf, cioppino or anything in a saute pan.

"It'll change your life"...Cirino's Bloody Mary Mix was created in 1983 by chef/owner Jerry Cirino at Cirino's Bar & Grill in Nevada City, CA. He touted that his version of the drink would, in fact, "change your life". He wasn't too far off. Our Bloody Mary drinks became so wildly popular, as did the demand to bottle the mix and offer it "to go" that we decided to listen to our loyal customers and as a result, we are serving 45 states and 6 countries. Today, we are still proudly making every bottle "in -house", each by hand...the very same quality and flavor we began with all those years ago. Our name is on the label. Our customers deserve the best. We've changed tens of thousands of lives...you could be next. It would be our honor and our pleasure. Salute!

name: Original U.S. WWII USMC M1 McCord Helmet with HBT Herringbone Twill P44 Utility Combat Uniform Collection [ON2934]
description:
Original Items: Only One Set Available. Purchased directly from a Veteran’s family this is a wonderful U.S. WWII United States Marine Corps set comprised of the following pieces:

• Size 40” WW2 USMC US Marine Corps P44 USMC Combat Uniform Field Utility Jacket in Olive Drab. It is dated 1944. This loose fitting sage green herringbone twill (HBT) cotton jacket features, original “doughnut hole” USMC buttons, gas flap, chest pocket with flap, internal breast pocket and stenciled black USMC EGA insignia. Offered in near excellent condition.

• Size 32” WW2 USMC US Marine Corps P44 USMC Combat Uniform Field Utility pants in Olive Drab. These loose fitting sage green herringbone twill (HBT) cotton pants feature, original “doughnut hole” USMC buttons, hip pockets, two open rear pockets. Offered in near excellent condition.

• Original WWII USMC 1944 M1 McCord Front Seam Helmet with 1943 Westinghouse Liner with Cover. The U.S. WWII M-1 helmet was only produced from 1941 to 1945. The first production batch resulted with over 323,510 M-1 helmets before the start of the American involvement in the war. This helmet is stamped "124" which indicates the approximate manufacture date of April 1942.

The Ordnance Department selected McCord Radiator and Manufacturing Company of Detroit Michigan to produce the steel M1 helmet bodies. These bodies were made from a single piece of Hadfield Manganese steel that was produced by the Carnegie-Illinois & Sharon Steel Corporations. Each completed raw M-1 helmet shell weighed 2.25 lbs each.

The later M-1 helmet shells had a set of swivel (movable) chinstrap loops called “bales” and a stainless steel rim. These rims were both rust resistant and had "non-magnetic qualities" that reduced the chance of error readings when placed around certain sensitive equipment (such as a compass).

This helmet is a fine example and still retains all of its original WW2 parts and the shell has all original "corked" grain paint.

The liner is correct “high pressure” WWII issue and stamped with a W for the Westinghouse Electric Co Manufactured in Pittsburgh, Pennsylvania this "high pressure" manufactured M-1 helmet liner is identified by an embossed "W" in the crown (which is still Westinghouse's logo to this day). Westinghouse was the largest M-1 helmet liner producer and had two production divisions; Micarta and Bryant Electric. The Micarta Division produced about 13,000,000 M-1 helmet liners and the Bryant Electric Division about 10,000,000. Westinghouse Electric Company started M-1 helmet liner delivery in May 1942. Westinghouse did have a contract to producce airborne liners and converted an unknown amount to airborne configuration. Westinghouse discontinued production around August 17, 1945 when the war ended.

This true almost unissued US WWII M-1 helmet liner be identified through the frontal eyelet hole. Other correct WW2 features include cotton herringbone twill (HBT) cloth suspension dated 1943. This HBT suspension is held tightly within the M-1 helmet liner by rivets and a series of triangular "A" washers. The three upper suspension bands are joined together with a shoestring. This way the wearer could adjust the fit. The leather liner chinstrap is the early war style but is broken.

The shell chin strap is original and the helmet cover is original 1953 issue USMC in excellent condition!

This is a wonderful near excellent condition genuine WW2 U.S.M.C set that will fill the gap in any pacific theatre collection.

name: Antique Wooden Hand-Crank Coffee Mill
description:
This Adventure Emporium listing is for ONE Antique Coffee Mill.

It’s hard to part with this one!

A great conversation piece on any coffee table, this is the perfect gift for an antique collector looking to add a quirky piece to their collection or the entrepreneur coffee aficionado who wants a unique piece of history to add character to their coffee shop.

This Antique Coffee Mill was made by hand with fingertip tenons joining the maple wood panels at each corner of the box. The mill can be hand-cranked by holding the ornate side handle and turning the elegantly curved rotating gear handle. The decorative shield-shaped iron panel on top houses the gear handle and the access port for pouring in the coffee beans. The inner gear mechanism would be adjusted for coarse or fine grounds with the top wing nut. The mill includes a pull-out drawer with a small iron handle that can be removed to dump fresh-ground coffee into a filter.

MEASUREMENTS:

•	Height: 13"
•	Width: 7”
Box:
•	Height: 6.25
•	Width: 5.75
Drawer:
•	Outside Length: 5.3”
•	Outside Width: 5”
•	Inside Depth: 1.5”

DISCLAIMER:

This item is sold AS IS!

The coffee mill is still functional although we do not recommend using it to grind coffee for consumption. The mill has not been tested for effective grinding of coffee beans.

The access port cover can be opened. Please do not insert anything into the opening to avoid finger injury from the inner gear mechanism.

This item is worn with age, is made of unsealed, unvarnished wood (which means that you can later stain and varnish it any way you like), and has imperfections such as a little rust on the iron components, but this adds character and should not get worse if kept indoors. The top is a little loose and there are cracks on the base edges of the box. With careful use for decorative purposes, this piece will age well.

Message shopkeep for additional details.

name: Sunstone Pendulum with Hamsa and Root Chakra Stones
description:
This sunstone pendulum has amazing flash, a truly stunning piece all by itself. It is accompanied by a silver Hamsa and red jasper, carnelian and onyx. On the end is a small clear quartz ball to hold on to while dowsing. The entire pendulum is approximately 10 inches in length.

Pendulums have long been used for Divination, it is an ancient technique used to access unknown information from one's higher self, the universe etc. The basic dowsing pendulum consists of a weight and a chain. This combination creates a radiesthetic reaction in the hands of a "sensitive" person. In essence it will move in various directions to give an answer to a specific question posed.

This pendulum has been cleared and infused with Reiki. It comes in a pouch with an explanation of the stones' metaphysical properties and how to cleanse, program, and use your new Pendulum.

Please note that Divination and the Metaphysical are a very spiritual based practice. I make no claims that this or any other tool of divination or the metaphysical can diagnose or cure any ailments or truly "predict" the future. We all have free will and the choice to choose our destinies.

Carnelian works with the sacral chakra. It grounds and anchors in to the present surroundings.It clarifies perception and dispels apathy.

Red Jasper works with the root or base chakra. It grounds energy and aids in dream recall. It also helps rectify unjust situations.

Onyx is strength giving and very helpful during difficult or confusing times. It helps center and align with the higher power.

name: 2016 Astrology Guide
description:
The 2016 Celestial Spheres Sky Journal is an A5, easy to carry, daily and monthly astrology guide and calendar. The booklet features exquisite design and high-end custom publishing with illustrations from an 1820's astronomy textbook.

Cycles of time constantly unfold as the Sun, the Moon and the planets travel through the zodiac. Make notes using this simple and practical guide, as you follow their divinely scripted pathway through the celestial realms.

A guide to planetary symbolism, Moon cycles, Moon signs, void Moon and retrograde planets. Each month is displayed listing the daily position of the Sun and the Moon, the Full, New and Quarter Moon days, eclipses and retrograde planetary stations. Space is provided to jot down your own notes and observations.

When observing planetary cycles, you are tuning in to a beautiful, organic and ancient wisdom.

Included in the monthly calendar pages~

★ Full Moons, New Moons, Dark Moon times and Quarter Moon dates
★ Sabian Symbols for the Full and New Moons
★ Equinoxes, Solstices and Eclipse dates
★ Daily Sun and Moon signs (and degrees)
★ Daily Void Moon Times
★ All planetary retrograde dates (including Mercury, Venus, Jupiter, Saturn, Uranus, Neptune and Pluto)

Included in the guide pages~

☆ An explanation of the annual and monthly solar and lunar cycles, their symbolism and conscious time-keeping
☆ A guide to daily Moon energy codes according to zodiac sign and what activities are best suited
☆ How to use the Void Moon times to maximise micro-time capsules
☆ Symbolism of the planets as a guide for Retrograde Phases
☆ Monthly wellness notes according to Sun Signs of the Zodiac
☆ Astrological sign archetypes and characteristics

~ This calendar uses the tropical zodiac at noon GMT/UT ~

name: Spalted Sycamore Bowl
description:
Spalted Sycamore wood hand turned & finished bowl.  This is a beautiful piece of wood with some lovely spalting and quilting giving it an iridescent look.  It's finished with wax.

170mm diameter x 40mm high

All of the wood I use for my bowls comes from trees grown in the UK from sustainable sources.  The majority of it comes from my own garden – either trimmings or from trees removed as part of regular management.  Other wood comes from friends and neighbours who have had trees trimmed or removed.  A few bowls are made from wood bought from a supplier of bowl blanks – this is not a source I use any more, not for any environmental or other concerns, simply because I have a very good stock of more local wood now.  For the future I intend that all of the wood I use will be local and that the source and reason for felling will be verifiable.  This provenance is important to me as far too man y trees are felled for no good reason without being replaced.

My bowls are all turned on a lathe and finished by hand.  They are not perfect specimen pieces – they are real pieces of wood complete with marks, knots, cracks, twists and warps.  Many are turned ‘green’ (which means fairly fresh after being cut and still quite wet) and as such will continue to dry and find their final shape for some time yet.  This is a natural process and only adds to the unique character of each individual piece.

They are all finished with either wax or oil, see the in individual descriptions for each bowl.  They are ‘food safe’ for use as fruit bowls but I would not recommend using them to eat from.  They would benefit from the occasional waxing (standard furniture wax is fine) or oiling (walnut oil from the supermarket is good), just a light wipe is fine to keep them looking their best.

Don’t  soak in water (wipe with a damp cloth and dry straight away) and avoid direct sunlight for any extended period.  Do pick them up regularly and hold them, feel them and enjoy them!

name: Turkish scarf / daisy floral black kerchief / organic cotton vintage fabric / handicraft Turkish lace oya / foulard / yemeni / unique gift
description:
TURKISH SCARF - DAISY SHAPE OYA - TURKISH HANDICRAFT VINTAGE COTTON BLACK SCARF

This beautiful handmade Turkish traditional scarf, called "yemeni". Its borders are adorned with Turkish lace technique that is called "oya".

OYA is a kind of hardly handicraft traditional art that is made by especially Turkish women. Like all other Traditional handmade arts, it is dying as well, because of advancing technology. so you have an opportunity to keep the magnificent tradition and to support these women who have such talent making these gorgeous scarfs by purchasing one of them.

and also this stunning laced, floral printed, black, Organic cotton scarf is taken out from Turkish wedding chests from 1980s. this feature is my scarf's difference from all other Turkish scarf sellers on etsy! because; nowadays it isin't being produced so high quality organic cotton fabrics in Turkey. They are generally cotton/synthetic fabrics. so the products of 1980s are rather requested. and i 've looked for and collected of them for you.

its condition is as good as new, well-preserved in the dowry chest. even though it is aprox. 40 years old, it is quite clean as like as new. it has no tear or stain.

It can be used as a shoulder shawl or a head scarf, or with the V turned to the front. it is just suitable for hippie or gypsy or boho styles and so forth. Complete your style with this very versatile fashion accessory!

PRODUCT DETAILS:

Material : Easy dry ,light weight and soft organic cotton fabric.
Color : black base - the actual colors may differ on your screen due to monitor settings .
shape : square
measurements: 90 x 90 cm / 35.4 x 35.4 inch

Handmade very good care in smoke-free and pet-free home

CARE INSTRUCTIONS:
Handwash gently in cool or lukewarm water and lay flat to dry. Steam lightly if needed.

***

Please do not hesitate to contact with me for any questions.

Thank you for visiting TurkishAccesories store

name: Honey infused with Ghost Chilies and Coconut
description:
Spicy honey is a unique condiment great on cheese plates, toast, pizza, wings, eggs, peanut butter, and even ice cream. The honey evens out the heat from the chilies and lets you enjoy their unique flavor profiles while still giving you bit of a kick. Great for the heat seekers in your life.

The hottest of our flavors, Ghost Chilies with Coconut is a strong competitor for the tastiest. The Coconut imparts an almost chocolatey flavor into the honey that compliments the hotter Ghost Chili perfectly. Previously known as the hottest pepper in the world, the mildness of this condiment is a testament to the true wonder of Spicy Honeys. Most wouldn’t dare eating even the smallest sliver of these chilies, but add honey and you’ve got a perfectly balanced sweet and spicy condiment that lets you enjoy a bit of heat and the true flavor profile of the chili.

Ingredients: 12oz Pure USA Honey, Ghost Chilies, “Baker’s Sweetened Coconut”

name: Honey infused with Habaneros
description:
Spicy honey is a unique condiment great on cheese plates, toast, pizza, wings, eggs, peanut butter, and even ice cream. The honey evens out the heat from the chilies and lets you enjoy their unique flavor profiles while still giving you bit of a kick. Great for the heat seekers in your life.

Our original creation, the Habanero Honey just might be our favorite. Born out of a late night snacking session eating pickled habaneros, that while super fruity and tasty were just too hot to enjoy. As if by fate, I caught a bottle of honey in the corner of my eye and remembered sugars help extinguish capsacin burns. I drenched my peppers and tortilla chips in it and “Wow,” I couldn’t beleive how tasty and mild my peppers had become. Our only honey not featuring other ingredients this flavor is great on almost anything and great for cooking when you want a little extra heat.

Ingredients: 12oz Pure USA Honey, Habaneros

name: Purple Bible Study Notes Printable for traveler's notebook and Fauxdori, Faithdori, Bible journaling, Bible art journaling
description:
This is a digital file for a standard size fauxdori or travelers notebook.  The file will print on 8.5x11 paper and will need trimmed to size (2.75 bottom margin).  The file should be printed front and back, trimmed, and then stapled together in the center to form a booklet.

You are not purchasing a finished product.  You must download the file to print your own insert.

The Bible study planner is great for keeping track of your notes in personal or small group Bible studies.  It can be used if you are studying a book of the Bible, or if you are studying a separate book or devotional.  There is a box at the top to list the book and/or author.  On the left side of the page is a box titled "Big Idea." Below that is a box marked "Key Passages," a perfect place to write in a Bible verse or page number.  On the right side of the page is a Notes column.  And across the bottom is a white box for journaling inspiration.

Because I read my Bible and all other books on my Kindle, I needed a place to write my notes for Bible study where I could easily reference them.  And I'm always getting Bible journaling inspiration when I'm reading.  Now I have one place to keep them all.

If you would like the Bible Study Notes printable in a different color, please message me about a special order.

name: Lan Love Beauty I
description:
SWISS Ionen Schmuck das Original - "Mehr als nur Schmuck"
Jede Kette ein Unikat- Energie Ketten swissionenschmuck.ch

PRODUKTINFO
Als Hals oder Armbandkette gedacht

Materialien
Diverses Holzpulver, afrikanisches, Kuhhornpulver, Turmalinpulver, Infrarotpulver, Negativ-Ionenpulver, energetisiertes Wasser, Energetikum Tropfen.


Verarbeitung
Mit Liebe wird aus der Holzmasse jedes Kettenglied von Hand in seine Form geknetet. Alle Materialien werden vorab auf den Energielevel des Körpers ausgetestet.

Herstellung
Die Ketten werden von Hand in der Schweiz hergestellt.

Ionen-Eigenschaft
Alle Ketten haben einen Negativ-Ionenwert zwischen 5000-7000/cm3. Die genaue Anzahl ist mit einem Etikett an dem Schmuck versehen.

DIE POSITIVE WIRKUNG VON NEGATIV IONEN

Unser gesundheitliches Wohlbefinden und unsere Leistungsfähigkeit hängen zum grossen Teil auch von der Qualität der Luft ab, die wir einatmen. Diese Luft ist erfüllt mit sogenannten Ionen. Man unterscheidet hierbei Aufgrund deren Elektrischer Ladung zwischen Positiv- und Negativ-Ionen, wobei letzteres als für den Menschen gesundheitsfördernd gilt. Das Grundmaterial ist Holzpulver aus diversen Hölzer, welches mit verschiedenen Negativ-Ionenpulvern vermischt wird. Durch das Holz ist die Kette sehr leicht und kaum bis nicht spürbar, daher wird sie von unseren Kunden oft auch im Bett getragen.

Der Energieschmuck wirkt auf den Körper. Man kann innert Sekunden eine Verbesserung der Schmerzpunkte wahrnehmen.
Durch diverse Umwelteinflüsse, wie Elektrosmog, langes Arbeiten am Computer, Kunststoffe, Umweltgifte allgemein, Staubpartikel, Aufenthalt in geschlossenen Räumen werden dem Körper vermehrt pos. Ionen zugeführt, was zu einer Disbalance der Ionen im Organismus führt. Durch das Tragen einer SWISS Ionen Kette ist für die optimale Balance an neg. und pos. Ionen im Organismus gesorgt. Diese sollte bei etwa 60 zu 40 liegen. Durch eine erhöhte Anzahl von pos. Ionen im Organismus können sich Muskeln verkrampfen, Gifte ablagern, der Sauerstoff nicht voll verwertet werden und freie Radikale frei werden. Das Tragen des Schmuckes sorgt für eine zusätzliche Zufuhr an neg. Ionen was zu einer deutlichen Verbesserung des allgemeinen Wohlbefindens dient. Der Körper hat mehr Energie und regeneriert sich schneller und die Zellen können besser entgiftet werden, da Umweltgifte sich nicht mehr so gut andocken können. Die Ketten geben zwischen 5000-7000 neg. Ionen pro 3cm Luft ab und dies über Jahre.

name: Custom fleece loop-tie blankets
description: Winter is here! How about a nice double-layered, fine quality, extra warm fleece blanket to keep you warm.  They are made to order based on the ideas you give me for your personal blanket.  The possibilities are endless as fleece patterns range from solid colors to Disney characters to wildlife animals...prices vary depending on the fleece you choose.  I usually recommend doing either two solid fleece colors or one solid and one pattern.  These blankets are fine quality and I take the time to put great effort into making sure they will last. They are easy to clean via laundry machine.  Sizes range from 4ft blankets to 9 ft. Prices are subject to change based on the size and/or fleece pattern you choose. Message me for inquiries and quotes. If you aren't sure if the pattern you like exists, message me and I will let you know. $30 is not a fixed price. That is the cheapest blanket I've made - it's a starting price. Blankets may range from $30-60.  These prices may seem high but they cover the cost of supplies.  This craft is a hobby of mine so my goal isn't to overcharge anyone.

name: Atlas
description:
The power and strength both physically and mentally are what stand out to the viewer straight away followed closely by the attitude the physical gesture may suggest. Atlas is a fitting name for a Mustang as such strength is required to survive out in the wild , now more than ever.

Acrylic paint on stretched canvas with a varnish finish.

W 76 cm L 61 cm Depth 4.5 cm

Atlas was inspired by the effect of a documentary I watched about the wild Mustangs of North America and the trials they must endure daily to survive .
I used the knife a lot in this piece and I think it added a nice effect to the overall feel of the painting which for me is about having the strength to survive.

name: BEISTELLTISCH mit Mario Motiv aus Mosaiksteinen
description:
Der Beistelltisch im Mario Design ist DER Hingucker in jedem Wohnzimmer, der auch Nichtgamer begeistern dürfte.

Die Basiskonstruktion besteht aus Eichenholz und besitzt unter der Tischplatte eine Ablagefläche.
Die Tischplatte selbst wurde mit Mosaiksteinen aus Softglas besetzt und mit Wasser- wie Frostfester Fugenmasse bearbeitet.

Die Tischplatte besitzt eine Grösse von 89cm x 55cm, der Tisch ist 44cm hoch (Boden bis Oberkant Tischplatte).

Alles in allem benötigte isch 120 Arbeitsstunden um dieses schöne Stück fertig stellen zu können.

Selbstredent kann auf Bestellung auch ein neur Tisch angefertigt und das Motiv nach Wunsch gewählt werden. Die Lieferzeit für eine komplette Neubestellung liegt bei 4 Wochen.

name: Custom Superman vs Batman Custom Birthday Invitation - Personalized Printable DIGITAL FILE
description:
Welcome to Fehlinger Graphics!

This listing is for a 5x7 print ready digital file of a Custom Superman vs Batman Birthday Invitation. After ordering, this invitation will be personalized with your event details and then a digital file will be emailed to you. You can then print at the printer of your choice. Fehlinger Graphics also offers print and mail services upon request.


***NOTICE: This listing is for a digital file ONLY.
>>> NO PHYSICAL ITEMS WILL BE SHIPPED <<<

Why order a digital file?...
• Fast turnaround
• No shipping fees
• Save money by printing at home or send to your favorite print center
• Print exact number of invitations needed
• Ability to email to friends and family

---- How to Order - Superman vs Batman Birthday Party Invitation ----
1. Click "Add to Cart" to begin purchase process.

2. Add all of your event details in the "Note to Fehlinger Graphics" box at checkout.
Including:
• name
• age
• location / address
• day of week, date, time
• RSVP info (optional) - exact wording please

3. Once payment and all of your event details are received your invitation will be personalized. A high resolution NON-EDITABLE 5x7 digital jpg file will then be emailed to you within 1 to 3 business days.

4. Upon receipt, please review design and proof read invitation carefully for any spelling mistakes. If you are not completely satisfied let us know and we will make any small changes at no additional fees within 2 weeks of sale.

5. If acceptable, you are ready to print! You can print at home, send to your favorite print shop, or simply email out to friends and family!

For best results, print on white cardstock.

***Note that printed colors may not match exactly due to varieties in paper quality, computer monitor setting, and printer quality.

Please feel free to contact us with any questions about this Superman vs Batman Birthday Invitation!

Thanks!

description:
Beautiful speckled glass vase from Reijmyre glass works in Sweden. Perfect mint condition A+++

Reijmyre is one of Sweden oldest glass factory's. It was founded in 1810 and was the first company in Sweden to introduce pressed glass, way back in in the 1840s. Many famous designers have since worked for Reijmyre and their glass is admired and collected all over the world

Measures 17cm tall, approx 8cm at it's widest.

name: PORTRAIT aus Bügelperlen gesetzt. Einzigartig und speziell
description:
Wer ein ganz spezielles Geschenk für jemanden sucht der trifft mit einem Portraitbild der ganz besonderen Art voll ins Schwarze.
Ein Portrait aus Bügelperlen sieht nicht nur ganz speziell aus, sondern versprüht auch einen besonderen Charme.

Dieses Beispiel misst 60cm in der Breite und 91cm in der Höhe und besteht aus über 21000 Bügelperlen. 130 Arbeitsstunden waren nötig um dieses Bild fertig zu stellen.

Format und Bildgrösse richten sich nach den Massen des gewünschten Bildrahmens und kann nach belieben angepasst werden. Bügelperlenmotive erlauben eine Toleranz von 5 Millimetern was eine Größen Anpassung relativ unkompliziert gestaltet.

Für eine saubere Umsetzung dient als Basis ein digitales Bild mit möglichst hoher Auflösung. Dieses wandle ich dann in Pixel um, lege zur Orientierung einen Raster darüber und fertige zum Schluss einen Ausdruck (Minimum A3) an der mir dann als Vorlage dient.

name: Original U.S. Naval Aviator Type G-1 Leather Flight Jacket - Vietnam War (Size 42) [GLT2004]
description:
Original Item: One-of-a-kind. Dating from the Vietnam war this excellent condition leather G-1 flight jacket with fur collar is size 42” and has a patch on the left breast for the Helicopter Combat Support Squadron 2 that reads “HC-2 Fleet Angels”. Also, on left breast is the name of the Naval Aviator that wore this jacket, the patch reads DICK LAVIGNE, FLEET ANGEL.

On the right breast is a very rare ANDROS RANGES AUTEC Patch. Anyone who has spent much time around either submarines or the Bahamas is likely to have heard of something called AUTEC. Not many people know much about it since it involves submarines and testing to ensure the subs and their weapons work well. AUTEC’s main base is on Andros Island, a short flight from Nassau. A key part of AUTEC is its North Atlantic Treaty Organization (NATO) Naval Forces Sensor and Weapons Accuracy Check Sites (FORACS), known as NFA. AUTEC was picked for its access to the Tongue of the Ocean, a remarkable site protected from the open Atlantic so ambient noise is at a minimum.

On the right arm is a third patch that reads NAVAL UNDERWATER SYSTEMS CENTER.

The "G-1" military flight jacket is the commonly accepted name for the fur-lined-collar World War II-era flight jacket of the United States Navy, Marine Corps, and Coast Guard. The G-1 remains a current uniform-issue item in naval aviation for officer and enlisted aviation personnel on flying status in the U.S. Navy, U.S. Marine Corps and U.S. Coast Guard (i.e., Naval Aviator, Naval Flight Officer, Naval Flight Surgeon, Naval Aircrewman, etc.) and is arguably best known as the leather flight jacket as worn by Tom Cruise in the film Top Gun.

description:
Куколка-мотанка на счастье или Доля. Одна из самых «светлых» традиционных кукол. Приносит счастье своей обладательнице и помогает найти свое призвание в жизни. Длинная коса – символ женской силы, красоты и здоровья). Делается без использования иголки с добрыми мыслями и пожеланиями :) Хотите впустить счастье в свой дом? Пригласите в него куколку-мотанку Счастье ;)
Куколка на счастье имеет своеобразные лапоточки; они помогают ей на пути поиска счастья. Коса как символ женского начала и женской силы обозначает здоровье, достаток, красоту и долгую жизнь. Лучше всего, если коса направлена вверх и вперёд - к новым достижениям и новым успехам (также это делает куклу более устойчивой, она как бы опирается на свою косу).
В русских народных сказках, где герои ищут своё счастье, Долюшка упоминается как куколка-помощница. Так и сейчас считается, что если носить такую куколку с собой, то будет сопутствовать успех, и владелица найдёт своё счастье.
Я с радостью сделаю для Вас и ваших близких такой оберег по вашим предпочтениям, например, в цвете. Пишите свои пожелания, пусть и в вашем доме царит гармония.
Размер 8 см

Doll motanka happiness or share. One of the "light" of traditional dolls. It brings happiness and helps its owner to find his calling in life. Long braid - a symbol of female strength, health and beauty). Done without the use of needles with good thoughts and wishes :) Do you want to let happiness into your home? Invite to a doll-motanku Happiness;)
Dolly has a peculiar happiness boots; they help her in the search for happiness. Spit as a symbol of femininity and feminine power represents health, wealth, beauty and long life. It is best if the braid is directed upward and forward - to new achievements and new successes (as it makes the doll more sustainable, it seems to be based on his scythe).
In Russian folk tales, where the characters seek happiness, Dolyushka referred to as a doll-assistant. So now it is believed that if you wear a doll with them, it will be successful, and the owner will find their happiness.
I am happy to do for you and your loved ones a guardian to your preference, for example, in color. Write your wishes even in your house harmony reigns.

They come in a 1oz glass jar with a dropper to help you apply the oil to your manly hedge and get you on your way to having the beard of a king!
The Grizzly is a cedarwood dominated oil that makes you feel like you just got done chopping down a forest and building your own log cabin!
If you want to feel like you're on the beach in a sunny paradise sipping on your favorite drink, you want the Citrus Om.
Or if a minty refreshing smell that really invigorates your skin and mane, the Hibernis Barba is just for you!

name: Doll-motanka Pregnancy Motherhood/Кукла-мотанка Беременность-Материнство
description:
Кукла-мотанка Беременность-Материнство.
Кукла Беременность является обереговой куклой. Она олицетворяет образ беременной женщины. У нее в животике живет малыш,который прочно спрятан в пенальчик и завязан пояском, что символизирует пуповину. Кукла очень мудро устроена. В её животике находится младенчик. Внутреннее устройство животика куклы повторяет устройство женского организма: матка, плацента, эмбрион. Творя эту куклу с дочерью, мать объясняла дочке строение женского тела в игровой форме.Лента в виде креста красного цвета, находящаяся на животике является дополнительной защитой. Такая кукла у древних славян изготавливалась не только для женщин,которые долго и безуспешно пытались зачать дитя, но и для тех, кто уже носит ребенка под сердцем.
Кукла Беременность помогает легче перенести роды. По преданию предков, в момент родов, пенальчик с малышом развязывался, и ребенок извлекался оттуда. Этот обряд помогал родить здорового и красивого дитя.
Данный оберег нужно поставить на виду, но когда женщина родит,куклу нужно спрятать.
Если беременность протекала хорошо, куколку передавали из поколения в поколение.
Куклу давали детям в игру, чтобы образ материнства проникал в их сознание.
У куколки не руки, а только имитация рук. Почему она делается без рук? Потому, что беременной нельзя физически работать – это может навредить плоду
Размер куколки 22 см.

Doll-motanka Pregnancy Motherhood.
Doll Pregnancy is a ritual doll. It represents the image of a pregnant woman. She lives in the tummy baby, which is firmly tucked away in penalchik and tied a belt that symbolizes the umbilical cord. The doll is very wisely arranged. Her tummy is baby. Internals tummy doll repeating unit of the female body: the uterus, placenta, embryo. Creates the doll with her daughter, the mother of a daughter explained the structure of the female body in the game forme.Lenta a red cross, located on the tummy is additional protection. This doll was made by the ancient Slavs not only for women, who had unsuccessfully tried to conceive a child, but also for those who already has a child at heart.
Doll Pregnancy makes easier to transfer labor. According to legend, the ancestors, at the time of delivery, with the baby penalchik untied, and the child was removed from there. This ritual helped give birth to a healthy and beautiful baby.

name: Fire Face
description:
Fire and flames that hide an image of a face within it. This image that provokes the search for shapes within shapes. This fiery photograph highlights the colours and textures that nature provides for us to marvel at.

Pareidolia is a psychological phenomenon involving a stimulus, in this case an image, wherein the mind perceives a familiar pattern of something where none actually exists. Common examples are perceived images of animals, faces, or objects in the image.

Decorate your home or office with this beautifully enlivening image that allows the viewer to feel inspired and impassioned. Drink in nature and her beauty through my gaze and enjoy.

name: Seahorse pendant - Animal Jewelry - Sterling Silver Ocean Creature
description:
Seahorse pendant accurately sculpted from  a real seahorse in the genus Hippocampus.

3D printed and lost wax cast in solid sterling silver.

This pendant is 1-1/2 inches tall (4 cm)
It comes with a matching sterling silver chain.

Seahorse is the name given to 54 species of small marine fishes in the genus Hippocampus. "Hippocampus" comes from the ancient Greek word hippos meaning "horse" and kampos meaning "sea monster". Seahorses sport a segmented bony armour, an upright posture and a curled prehensile tail.

The short-snouted seahorse (Hippocampus hippocampus) is a species of seahorse in the family Syngnathidae. It is endemic to the Mediterranean Sea and parts of the North Atlantic, particularly around Italy and the Canary Islands. Colonies of the species have recently been discovered in the River Thames around London. Their preferred habitat is shallow muddy waters, estuaries or seagrass beds.  (courtesy Wikipedia)

name: Original U.S. WWII China Burma India Theater A2 Leather Flight Jacket (Size 40) [GLT2003|
description:
Original Item: One-of-a-kind. This is a nice but well worn A2 leather flight jacket issued to a pilot who served in the Pacific Theatre during WW2. It is good condition in a large size 40 chest. There is wear evident in the leather with fraying with and holes in cotton waist band and cuffs, but overall it is solid and wearable.

The best aspect of this incredible jacket is the embroidered U.S. eagle on the left breast along with a genuine CBI patch on the left shoulder along with a set of Captains bars.

The Type A-2 leather flight jacket is a military flight jacket closely associated with World War II U.S. Army Air Forces pilots, navigators and bombardiers, who often decorated their jackets with squadron patches and elaborate artwork painted on the back. Sometimes casually referred to as a bomber jacket, its original designation was "Jacket, Pilot's (summer)", and its wartime usage was limited neither to pilots nor to bomber crews. The A-2 jacket was awarded to an Army Air Forces officer upon completion of basic flight training, and always before graduating to advanced training. No standard system of distribution was used, though generally airmen lined up in front of boxes containing jackets of various sizes and given the appropriate size jacket by the base quartermaster. A-2s were exclusive to commissioned officers until early in World War II, when also issued to enlisted aircrews. The A-2 was a treasured item to the airman and was worn with as much pride as his wings. As airmen progressed through various duty stations they often added and removed squadron patches, rank marks, and occasionally elaborate artwork depicting the type of aircraft they flew or a copy of the artwork painted on their airplane. Bomber crews often added small bombs to the right front of their jackets indicating the number of missions they had flown. As a result, many jackets ended up with numerous stitch marks as patches of various sizes were removed and replaced when the owner changed units. Unlike Navy aviators, who often wore the patches of every squadron they had ever flown with, AAF personnel could only display the patch of their current assignment. The emblem of the Army Air Forces was often sewn, painted, or applied by decal on the left shoulder, while the shield of the specific Air Force (5th, 8th, etc.) was often displayed on the right. Despite the A-2's becoming a symbol of the American pilot, in 1943 General H. H. "Hap" Arnold canceled any further leather jacket contracts in favor of newer cloth-shell jackets like the B-10 and B-15. Needless to say, Arnold's popularity with his airmen was not improved by his decision. Even after the transition to cloth, existing units could still order replacement A-2s, keeping production going well into 1944. And it was impossible to prevent airmen from continuing to obtain and wear the style – as demonstrated by the large number of photos clearly showing Korean War pilots of F-82's and F-86's still wearing the original A-2 issued to them a decade earlier, or newer jackets made to fit their current sizes. Fighter pilots, who often had heated cockpits, could wear the A-2 into combat more easily. Some jackets had a map of the mission area sewn into the lining, which could be used (in theory) for navigation if shot down. Some jackets (famously, those from the China Burma India Theater, and of the Flying Tigers) had a "Blood chit" sewn on the lining or outer back, printed on cloth, which promised certain rewards to civilians who aided a downed airman. In certain ETO units and possibly elsewhere a prerogative of the fighter ace was a red satin lining which was added on confirmation of his fifth aerial kill. Early wartime pictures show entire bomber crews outfitted with A-2s, although at altitude in a bomber they probably weren't too useful. The pilot and copilot had primitive cabin heat on some aircraft and would wear the A-2, while the rest of the bomber crew usually wore heavier fleece-lined Type B-3 or ANJ-4 (and later B-9 and B-11 parkas) which were warmer and better suited to long hours in the severe cold. However, period photos do show A-2s worn by crew underneath heavy outer garments, and candid on-base photos often show crewmen of all ranks in A-2s. A warm and comfortable mouton collar was an addition authorized in mountainous C-B-I commands.

name: The Hair Fader -NEW to the Market- Hair Clipper Guard | Guide | Hair Clippers
description:
Do you want to stop paying for your fade haircuts?

     The Hair Fader is your key to stop paying for your fade haircuts - period.

With the Hair Fader, nearly everyone can cut fade haircuts, even a child.
Don't pay for your next fade haircut. For the cost of approximately 1 barber visit, you can purchase your Hair Fader today and you will never have to pay for your fade haircuts again.

Search the web for our videos and watch a child, with no barber experience, cut a perfect fade!

So Easy, So Quick, So Perfect and So Simplified!

This listing is for 1 Hair Fader Attachment Guide
1 Hair Fader Attachment Guide with the dimensions of a #1 guard to a #5 guard within 1.5" travel distance.

Will the Hair Fader fit on your current clippers?

The Hair Fader has a universal fit that is designed to fit on a wide range of clippers. Nearly all of Wahl©, Oster© and Conair©. On the left side of this page, there is an illustration of clipper blades in which the Hair Fader will fit.

If you are not sure if the Hair Fader will fit your current hair clippers, please contact us and we will be glad to confirm if the Hair Fader will fit your clippers.


An Array of Benefits!

Convenient & Time Saving

Cutting a perfect fade/taper/blend style haircut has never been so easy and so fast!

With the Hair Fader, you can cut your own hair at home! Quickly and easily!

If your hand and eye coordination isn't what you would like it to be, no worries! The Hair Fader is so easy to use, nearly any one can cut a perfect fade/taper/blend haircut.

If you already cut your hair at home and have extraordinary hand and eye coordination, the Hair Fader can still save you time. Cut your fade within minutes!
The Hair Fader does all the work!

Money Saving

If you frequent the barber to get your fade haircut, you are probably spending an average of about $20 per haircut.

Wouldn't you like to use that money for something else? Anything else?

Once you use the Hair Fader, you will see and feel how easy it to use.

Because it is so easy to use, you can have nearly anyone give you a perfect fade haircut.
No more handing over money to the barber

Clip a Hair Fader onto almost any home use hair clippers and you will no longer need to frequent the barber for your fade haircuts.

Reliance and Precision

The Hair Fader has a patented function that prevents you from cutting an inconsistent fade haircut.
Its patented perpetual elevating function guides the clipper blades for you.

The precision of the Hair Fader is phenomenal. While the Hair Fader is in action, each and every proceeding hair strand is cut at a consistently higher length. For this reason,
1 Hair Fader equals over 1,000 ordinary clipper guards.

NOTE: Although the Hair Fader substantially simplifies cutting a fade/taper haircut, it is highly recommended that you do not use it on yourself, by yourself. The Hair Fader is recommended for ages 16+.

*Additional time was required to trim below and above the fade section.
